Death of the bear market
Artwork by Mannay (2022)

————————————————————

This illustration was created for the #benjaminkato art competition. The artwork is self explanatory, it represents my take on the death of the bear market. Apes strong together.

————————————————————

Artwork size : 5400 × 6750 px
